---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
<MainLayout title="Managed IT Services | Blue Cap IT — Your Outsourced IT Department" description="Blue Cap IT provides managed IT services including remote monitoring, helpdesk support, patch management, backup & disaster recovery, Microsoft 365 management, vCIO services, and more.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <img src="/images/managed-services-hero.jpg" alt="Real-time monitoring dashboard showing IT service metrics and analytics" style="width:100%;height:auto;max-height:340px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:1rem;margin-bottom:2rem;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);" />
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> Managed IT Services</div>
      <div class="section-label">Managed Service Provider</div>
      <h1>Managed IT <span class="grad">Services</span></h1>
      <p class="section-sub">Blue Cap IT acts as your complete outsourced IT department. We proactively monitor, manage, and support your entire technology environment — so you can focus on running your business.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- WHY MANAGED IT -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Why Managed IT</div>
          <h2>Proactive IT Management.<br/><span class="grad">Not Break-Fix.</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub">Instead of waiting for things to break, Blue Cap IT continuously monitors your systems, applies updates, and resolves issues before they impact your team. You get enterprise-level IT support at a predictable monthly cost.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="why-list">
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:bar-chart-3" /></div>
            <div><h4>24/7 Monitoring</h4><p>We monitor your servers, workstations, and network devices around the clock. If something goes wrong, we know about it before you do.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:wallet" /></div>
            <div><h4>Predictable Costs</h4><p>Flat monthly pricing means no surprise IT bills. Budget confidently with a clear, transparent cost structure.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:rocket" /></div>
            <div><h4>Reduced Downtime</h4><p>Proactive maintenance and rapid response keep your team productive and your systems running smoothly.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:handshake" /></div>
            <div><h4>A True IT Partner</h4><p>We're not just a vendor — we're an extension of your team. We learn your business and align technology with your goals.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICE CARDS -->
  <section id="services" style="background:var(--surface);">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
        <div class="section-label">Our Managed IT Services</div>
        <h2>Everything Your Business Needs.<br/><span class="grad">One Provider.</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="products-grid">
        <div id="rmm" class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:activity" /></div>
          <h3>Remote Monitoring &amp; Management</h3>
          <p>24/7 monitoring of your servers, workstations, and network devices. We detect and resolve issues proactively — often before your team even notices a problem.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="helpdesk" class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:headphones" /></div>
          <h3>Helpdesk Support</h3>
          <p>Your employees get fast, friendly IT support when they need it. Whether it's a password reset, software issue, or hardware question — we're a phone call or email away.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="patching" class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:refresh-cw" /></div>
          <h3>Patch Management</h3>
          <p>We keep your operating systems, applications, and firmware up to date with the latest security patches. Automated, tested, and applied on a schedule that works for your business.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="backup" class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:database-backup" /></div>
          <h3>Backup &amp; Disaster Recovery</h3>
          <p>Automated backups with tested recovery procedures. Your data is protected and recoverable — whether it's a deleted file or a full system failure.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="microsoft-365" class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:cloud" /></div>
          <h3>Microsoft 365 Management</h3>
          <p>We manage your Microsoft 365 environment — Exchange Online, Teams, SharePoint, OneDrive, and licensing. User provisioning, security configuration, and ongoing administration handled for you.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="network" class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:globe" /></div>
          <h3>Network Management</h3>
          <p>Firewalls, switches, Wi-Fi, and VPN — we design, deploy, and manage your network infrastructure to keep your business connected and secure.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="vcio" class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:brain" /></div>
          <h3>Virtual CIO (vCIO) Services</h3>
          <p>Get strategic IT leadership without the cost of a full-time executive. We help you plan technology roadmaps, set IT budgets, evaluate vendors, and align technology with your business goals.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- vCIO DETAIL SECTION -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="feature-row">
        <img src="/images/managed-services-vcio.jpg" alt="Team collaborating around a computer with strategy diagrams in the background" style="width:100%;height:100%;max-height:400px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:1rem;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);" />
        <div class="feature-text">
          <div class="section-label">Strategic IT Leadership</div>
          <h2>Virtual CIO <span class="grad">Services</span></h2>
          <p>Not every business needs a full-time CIO — but every business needs a technology strategy. Blue Cap IT's vCIO services give you an experienced IT leader who understands your business and helps you make smart technology decisions.</p>
          <ul class="feature-bullets">
            <li>Technology roadmap planning and budgeting</li>
            <li>Vendor evaluation and management</li>
            <li>IT policy development and compliance guidance</li>
            <li>Quarterly business reviews and reporting</li>
            <li>Strategic guidance for growth and scaling</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="cta-band">
    <div class="section-label">Let's Talk</div>
    <h2>Ready for Proactive<br/><span class="grad">IT Management?</span></h2>
    <p>Contact Blue Cap IT for a free quote. We'll assess your current IT environment and show you how managed services can reduce costs, improve uptime, and give you peace of mind.</p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost"><Icon name="lucide:phone" /> (410) 858-4031</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@bluecapit.com" class="btn-ghost"><Icon name="lucide:mail" /> info@bluecapit.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
